paragraphs.text:
%pyspark
from pyjake.sparkmodule import udf_dt2d, udf_dt2t, udf_delsec
from pyspark.sql.functions import udf
from pyspark.sql.types import DoubleType
import numpy as np

udf_il_scaler = udf(lambda v: v / 100000, DoubleType())
udf_sz_scaler = udf(lambda v: v / 100, DoubleType())
udf_log = udf(lambda v: np.log(v), DoubleType())

casa_srs = spark.read.parquet('hdfs:///nl/witlab/cas/casa_srs.parquet')

wt = spark.read.parquet('hdfs:///weather/witlab/wtob_f.parquet')\
          .withColumn('date', udf_dt2d('datetime'))\
          .withColumn('time', udf_dt2t('datetime'))\
          .withColumn('time', udf_delsec('time')).drop('datetime')

time = spark.read.parquet('hdfs:///sun/srs_min.parquet')

dataset = casa_srs.join(time, ['date', 'time'])

dataset.show(1)

%pyspark

spdf_train_b, spdf_test = dataset.randomSplit([0.7, 0.3], 5)
spdf_train, spdf_val = spdf_train_b.randomSplit([0.7, 0.3], 5)

pdf_train = spdf_train.toPandas()
pdf_val = spdf_val.toPandas()
pdf_test = spdf_test.toPandas()

x_train = np.array(pdf_train[['illum', 'solar_zenith', 'cct']])
y_train = np.array(pdf_train['uvi'])

x_val = np.array(pdf_val[['illum', 'solar_zenith']])
y_val = np.array(pdf_val['uvi'])

x_test = np.array(pdf_test[['illum', 'solar_zenith']])
y_test = np.array(pdf_test['uvi'])

print('x_train:', len(x_train), 'x_val:', len(x_val), 'x_test:', len(x_test))
print('y_train:', len(y_train), 'y_val:', len(y_val), 'y_test:', len(y_test))

paragraphs.title: init dataset
paragraphs.text:
%pyspark

from pyjake.sparkmodule import udf_dt2d, udf_dt2t, udf_delsec
from pyspark.sql.functions import udf
from pyspark.sql.types import DoubleType

udf_il_scaler = udf(lambda v: v / 100000, DoubleType())
udf_sz_scaler = udf(lambda v: v / 100, DoubleType())

cas = spark.read.parquet('hdfs:///nl/witlab/cas/whole_srs.parquet')\
           .withColumn('illum_s', udf_il_scaler('illum'))\
           .withColumn('sz_s', udf_sz_scaler('solar_zenith'))
time = spark.read.parquet('hdfs:///sun/srs_min.parquet')

cleandays = spark.read.parquet('hdfs:///dayday/clean_days.parquet')

dataset = cas.join(cleandays, 'date')\
             .join(time, ['date', 'time'])
dataset.show(1)

paragraphs.title: make dataset
paragraphs.text:
%pyspark
import numpy as np
spdf_train_b, spdf_test = dataset.randomSplit([0.7, 0.3], 5)
spdf_train, spdf_val = spdf_train_b.randomSplit([0.7, 0.3], 5)

pdf_train = spdf_train.toPandas()
pdf_val = spdf_val.toPandas()
pdf_test = spdf_test.toPandas()

x_train = np.array(pdf_train[['illum', 'swr', 'solar_zenith', 'relative']])
y_train = np.array(pdf_train['uvi'])

x_val = np.array(pdf_val[['illum', 'swr', 'solar_zenith', 'relative']])
y_val = np.array(pdf_val['uvi'])

x_test = np.array(pdf_test[['illum', 'swr', 'solar_zenith', 'relative']])
y_test = np.array(pdf_test['uvi'])

print('x_train:', len(x_train), 'x_val:', len(x_val), 'x_test:', len(x_test))
print('y_train:', len(y_train), 'y_val:', len(y_val), 'y_test:', len(y_test))
